Package: leiturgia
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: armhf
Maintainer: Dennis Arquillano <arquillanodennis@gmail.com>
Depends: python3, python3-pip, python3-venv, git, chromium-browser, openssl
Description: Live worship projection system for Raspberry Pi
 Leiturgia is a real-time, multi-channel projection app for church services.
 It manages hymns, lyrics, media, and program flow with a live operator console.
